Wortbaum is an Open Source application for writing books and magazines online.

== Features
None so far

== Future Features
* Manage Books, Chapters, Pages and freely definable elements like Characters
* Templates for those freely definable elements so that novels and non-fiction have their own set
* Multiple Users writing on one Book or Chapter
* Invite other users to a Book, Chapter or Page
* Account creation on the fly (start writing, invitees have an account)
* Export a Book to a git repository (e.g. for a customized jekyll fork)

== Technical notes

* Book and Chapter inherit from Page
* Note can be something like a charater description, reference or similar
  Can be referenced by several pages
* User, UserPagePermission
* Export ePub

